EDGE CASES / BEHAVIOR NOTES
---------------------------
- Chat session after successful job complete stays **running** so POST /input is allowed; failed job sets session **failed**.
- POST /input returns 409 if not running, not chat, or any job pending/assigned.
- Non-chat workflows on POST /sessions return 400 “Only workflow \"chat\" is supported in this release”.
- First pull moves session pending→running only when a job transitions from pending→assigned in that transaction branch.

